PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to the Hon. ROBERT M. THOMPSON, a Judge of the Ontario Court of Justice (General Division), who was required to relocate from the City of Brantford to the City of Owen Sound.

precis:
Order prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION
EXPENSES may be reimbursed to the Hon. ROBERT M. THOMPSON, a Judge of the
Ontario Court of Justice (General Division), who was required to relocate
from the City of Brantford to the City of Owen Sound.
